SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 2000Z DAILY
   09 AND 10 APR AND 111000Z TO 111800Z APR
   WITHIN 60 MILES OF 57-02.0N 009-07.4W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 612/10.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 111900Z APR.
